      <span class="block"><strong><i class="fa fa-map-marker"></i> Address:</strong> 4468 Wellington Street, Montreal, QC, Canada</span> <br/>
      <span class="block"><strong><i class="fa fa-phone"></i> Phone:</strong> <a class="addhover" href="tel:581-701-0303">581-701-0303</a></span> <br/>
      <span class="block"><strong><i class="fa fa-envelope"></i> Email:</strong> <a class="addhover" href="mailto:info@codeboxx.biz">info@codeboxx.biz</a></span> <br/>
    </div>
